      <div class="mainleft_title"> 
       <h1> 叙利亚总统阿萨德：中俄越强大 小国越安全 </h1> 
      </div> 
      <div class="mainleft_two"> 
       <div class="mainleft_from">
         作者：
        <a href="http://toutiao.weiyoubaba.com/m1675/">观察者网</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; 发布时间：2016-12-15
       </div> 
      </div> 
      <div class="mainleft_three"> 
       <p><span style="color: rgb(2, 30, 170);"><strong><span style="font-size:auto;">【文/观察者网 杜津】</span></strong></span></p>
       <p style="margin-top: 15px;">在4年半的苦战之后，昨天（12月14日）叙利亚政府军在俄罗斯的帮助下<a href="http://www.guancha.cn/global-news/2016_12_14_384235.shtml" target="_blank">收复阿勒颇</a>，惨遭恐怖分子荼毒的古城阿勒颇终于实现停火。叙利亚电视台播出的画面显示，当地居民走上街头，鸣枪跳舞庆祝和平，但大部分西方媒体却对此视而不见，反称当地“人道状况完全崩溃”。</p>
       <p style="margin-top: 15px;">叙利亚总统阿萨德本周接受“今日俄罗斯”电视台专访，就当前以及欧美在此间扮演的角色进行了分析。他指出，世界格局越平衡，对小国越有利，苏联解体后，美国一直处于独霸地位，中俄的崛起有助于改变这种局面，从而保证小国的安全。</p>
       <p style="margin-top: 15px; text-align: center;"><img data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wZ8jfcVwf7IibiaqvXRiaw8sDQicvtrOlF0TPu5PiaFiaT1ibIKlDy9prpsGTcIJ0p9mS0KZwz03RlPX2bqD14x4YWFow/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" width="550" height="309" style="border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle;" class="" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="0.5622389306599833" data-w="1197" /></p>
       <p style="margin-top: 15px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:auto; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">视频截图</span></p>
       <p style="margin-top: 15px; text-align: center;"><img data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wZ8jfcVwf7IibiaqvXRiaw8sDQicvtrOlF0TVMGP2zh8yTu2K3aSj2ZVibVpGLyQ1pfUfISzl5YGczBECh1pTjFsJyQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" style="border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle;" class="" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="1.6266666666666667" data-w="600" /></p>
       <p style="margin-top: 15px; text-align: left;"><iframe class="video_iframe" data-vidtype="1" style="   z-index:1; " height="375" width="500" frameborder="0" src="https://v.qq.com/iframe/preview.html?width=500&amp;height=375&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=u03555bmxbj" allowfullscreen=""></iframe><br />阿萨德认为，目前叙利亚的问题不是一个政府取代另一个政府，也不是武装军队之间的对抗，而是涉及到祖国的存亡。尽管痛苦，但叙利亚人还是在抗争。</p>
       <p style="margin-top: 15px;">除此之外，阿萨德斥责西方政客和媒体对待叙利亚的态度，“不管他们（媒体）提到什么，都是他们的面具，什么人权、平民、孩子，都是为了自己的目的服务的，他们的报道只是为了刺激公众，让公众支持他们插手叙利亚。”“在西方没有人真正了解，在叙利亚发生着什么”。</p>
       <p><br /></p>
       <hr style="font-size:auto; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" />
       <p style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; font-size:auto; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 128, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">07：</span><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">微博</span><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 104, 39); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">@观察者网</span><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">每月有</span><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 104, 39); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">不可描述</span><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">活动，老司机请提高警惕7215</span></strong></strong><br style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
       <p style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size:auto; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">转载规范请后台回复：<span style="max-width: 100%; font-size:auto; color: rgb(255, 127, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">转载</span></strong></span></p>
       <p style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(122, 79, 214); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">合作</strong></span><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size:auto; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(122, 79, 214); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></strong></span><span style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">/<span style="max-width: 100%; font-size:auto; color: rgb(0, 128, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">广告</span>/<span style="max-width: 100%; font-size:auto; color: rgb(61, 167, 66); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">投放<span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(2, 30, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">/沟通</strong></span></span></strong></span></span></p>
       <p style="font-size:auto; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; font-size:auto; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">7715：<span style="max-width: 100%; font-size:auto; color: rgb(255, 127, 170); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">pr@guancha.cn</span></strong></span></p>
